  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Echoes of the Sun is a first-person puzzle-platformer adventure game in a fantasy setting where you play as a brave girl with telekinesis, who tries to reach her parents.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Restore the environment</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extinguish fires, rebuild surroundings, and bring nature around you back to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/2b3556b4a771391d9caf4e0866aca185.poster.avif?t=1749477267\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/2b3556b4a771391d9caf4e0866aca185.webm?t=1749477267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/2b3556b4a771391d9caf4e0866aca185.mp4?t=1749477267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use Telekinesis</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manipulate objects, interact with mechanisms, and overcome obstacles. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/326d0930c8689955ccba4ea07f2be7d5.poster.avif?t=1749477267\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/326d0930c8689955ccba4ea07f2be7d5.webm?t=1749477267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/326d0930c8689955ccba4ea07f2be7d5.mp4?t=1749477267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solve Solar Magic Puzzles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use various magical devices to bend and combine energy beams, activating solar magic and gradually restoring the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/5390180a64b7c0a1150b9fd6a9bb7d7d.poster.avif?t=1749477267\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/5390180a64b7c0a1150b9fd6a9bb7d7d.webm?t=1749477267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/5390180a64b7c0a1150b9fd6a9bb7d7d.mp4?t=1749477267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore an Island Full of Ghosts and Mysteries</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you journey through Zoria, you'll encounter touching and chilling stories of ghosts filled with secrets and heartfelt confessions. Uncover the true story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/322e78e4118386723c46491798f2ab59.poster.avif?t=1749477267\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/322e78e4118386723c46491798f2ab59.webm?t=1749477267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/322e78e4118386723c46491798f2ab59.mp4?t=1749477267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Restoring the world is no easy task, but those who are brave and pure of heart will surely succeed. Let’s embark on this challenging journey with Mia and make Zoria  a brighter place!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Echoes of the Sun is a first-person puzzle-platformer adventure game in a fantasy setting where you play as a brave girl with telekinesis, who tries to reach her parents.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Restore the environment</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extinguish fires, rebuild surroundings, and bring nature around you back to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/2b3556b4a771391d9caf4e0866aca185.poster.avif?t=1749477267\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/2b3556b4a771391d9caf4e0866aca185.webm?t=1749477267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/2b3556b4a771391d9caf4e0866aca185.mp4?t=1749477267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use Telekinesis</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manipulate objects, interact with mechanisms, and overcome obstacles. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/326d0930c8689955ccba4ea07f2be7d5.poster.avif?t=1749477267\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/326d0930c8689955ccba4ea07f2be7d5.webm?t=1749477267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/326d0930c8689955ccba4ea07f2be7d5.mp4?t=1749477267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solve Solar Magic Puzzles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use various magical devices to bend and combine energy beams, activating solar magic and gradually restoring the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/5390180a64b7c0a1150b9fd6a9bb7d7d.poster.avif?t=1749477267\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/5390180a64b7c0a1150b9fd6a9bb7d7d.webm?t=1749477267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/5390180a64b7c0a1150b9fd6a9bb7d7d.mp4?t=1749477267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore an Island Full of Ghosts and Mysteries</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you journey through Zoria, you'll encounter touching and chilling stories of ghosts filled with secrets and heartfelt confessions. Uncover the true story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/322e78e4118386723c46491798f2ab59.poster.avif?t=1749477267\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/322e78e4118386723c46491798f2ab59.webm?t=1749477267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863040/extras/322e78e4118386723c46491798f2ab59.mp4?t=1749477267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Restoring the world is no easy task, but those who are brave and pure of heart will surely succeed. Let’s embark on this challenging journey with Mia and make Zoria  a brighter place!</p>",
